collection.name: Cryptoshack Club
collection.description:
ACTUAL OWNER COUNT: 1423 AS OF 05/12/2022. 79.5% STAKED

Cryptoshack is a collection of 5,855 fun-loving characters. Our community-driven project is a one-of-a-kind multi-dimensional play-to-earn game built on NFTWorlds by their top verified builder and our partners @entitybuilds. Multiple metaverses including an 18 hole golf course fully built and ready to play shortly after mint! Underground p2e world for our gophers. Golf, scavenger hunts, $WRLD token distribution.

The possibilities are truly endless inside of the Cryptoshack.

Managed by https://cryptoshack.club

Learn more in our whitepaper - https://crypto-shack.gitbook.io/cryptoshack-whitepaper/
